<br>
Not saying we all should bow down to the top 3 or 4 guilds and feel greatful for any kill we happen to get, but it is because of *them* that there exist sanity and fairness on the server, not the smaller guilds...The power guilds of the times keeps the piece moreso than anyone. Without their constant consideration of each other and the rules, The Rathe would suck major. The names of the guilds have changed over the years, but thank God the respect of each other on this server hasn't.<br>
